(901, 351, 'wp-svbtle-markdown', 'I''m a web and video craftsman currently living in Jarabacoa in the Dominican Republic and working as the Media Coordinator at <a href="http://doulosdiscovery.org">Doulos Discovery School</a>.\r\n\r\nHere''s a quick guide to the stuff you''ll find here;\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="My Story" href="http://josiahsprague.com/category/story/"><strong>Journal</strong></a> - Basically the story of my life; everything that I''m doing and learning. For stalkers trying to keep tabs on me.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a href="http://josiahsprague.com/category/dr/"><strong>Dominican</strong></a> - Stories about life in the Dominican Republic, my work at Doulos, and everything related to that. <a title="Support" href="http://josiahsprague.com/support/">Support me!</a></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a href="http://josiahsprague.com/category/thinking/"><strong>Thoughts</strong></a> - External processing. AKA preaching from my soapbox.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a href="http://josiahsprague.com/category/web/"><strong>Web Stuff</strong></a> - Technical, web industry related stuff. #nerdstatus</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>My Values</h2>\r\nIf people only remember two things about my life, they should be this;\r\n<blockquote>I am a great sinner, and Christ is a great savior.</blockquote>\r\nMy take on religion;\r\n<blockquote>Love God. Love others. Nothing else matters.</blockquote>\r\nOn being nice;\r\n<blockquote>Love is something more splendid and stern than mere kindness.</blockquote>\r\nThe way I think;\r\n<blockquote>Everything that is alive is changing. People, organizations, ideas, all of it. What is static is dead.</blockquote>\r\nWhen it comes to the work I do;\r\n<blockquote>If I''m going to spend a day cutting down a tree, I''ll spend two thirds of it sharpening my axe.</blockquote>'),
