(357, 1, '2013-03-06 13:22:55', '2013-03-06 13:22:55', '<div class="row-fluid">\r\n<div class="span8">\r\n<div class="hero-unit">\r\n<div class="spnsrmn" id="paypalform">My current need is to raise $920/month. Help me reach that goal by committing to support me monthly!\r\n<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick" /><input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="VRLUK2XKLFW7N" /><input type="hidden" name="on0" value="Monthly Support for Josiah Sprague" />\r\n<select name="os0"><option value="$10/month">$10/month</option><option value="$15/month">$15/month</option><option value="$20/month">$20/month</option><option value="$25/month">$25/month</option><option selected="selected" value="$50/month">$50/month</option><option value="$100/month">$100/month</option><option value="$150/month">$150/month</option><option value="$200/month">$200/month</option><option value="$250/month">$250/month</option></select><input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="USD" />\r\n<button class="btn btn-primary btn-large" name="submit" type="submit">Sponsor Me ▶</button>\r\n\r\n</form></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="span4"><img class="spnsrimg" alt="Josiah Sprague hiking at Magote" src="/images/portrait.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\nYou can also support me with a one-time donation. The bottom of this page lists some <a href="#give">other ways to give</a>. If you''ve arrived on this page without first hearing my vision for my ministry at Doulos, I invite you to <a href="http://josiahsprague.com/">read about my vision</a> first.\r\n<h2 id="goal">My Support Goal</h2>\r\nTo keep tuition costs at a minimum for families and sponsors, North American staff raises full support to work at Doulos. <b>I’ll need to raise about $920/mo, which is about $11,000/yr.</b>\r\n\r\nHere’s a breakdown of what I’ll need per month;\r\n<table class="table table-striped">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Need</th>\r\n<th>Estimated Amount</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tithe</td>\r\n<td>$92</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Rent</td>\r\n<td>$180</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Food</td>\r\n<td>$165</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cell Phone</td>\r\n<td>$15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mail</td>\r\n<td>$5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Insurance, Taxes and Fees</td>\r\n<td>$193</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Miscellaneous</td>\r\n<td>$45</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>School Loans</td>\r\n<td>$60</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Plane Tickets</td>\r\n<td>$165</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Total</th>\r\n<th>$920</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2 id="give">Ways to Give</h2>\r\nIf you''ve heard my vision and want to be a part of my team of supporters, here''s how you can do that:\r\n\r\n<b>If you want to sponsor me monthly,</b> you can give automatically via direct donation. To do so, download the <a href="http://josiahsprague.com/pdf/JosiahSpragueDonation.pdf">direct donation form</a> and mail it to the <a href="http://josiahsprague.com/support/#address">Minesota Doulos address</a>, below, along with your first check. Alternatively, you can set up your bank account to automatically send a check to that address every month. If you would prefer to donate online, you can set up a monthly donation via PayPal, <a href="http://josiahsprague.com/support/#paypalform">above</a>.\r\n\r\n<b>If you want to support me with a one time donation,</b> you can send a check to the Minesota Doulos address, or donate online via <a href="http://doulosdiscovery.org/support/donate/">the donation page on the Doulos website</a>.\r\n\r\nPlease make all checks payable to <i>Doulos Discovery Ministries</i> and, for tax purposes, please be sure to include a note along with your check indicating that the donation is for Josiah Sprague (it is best if this is a separate note, rather than being written on the memo line).\r\n\r\nPlease send Direct Donation Forms and checks to:\r\n<p id="address">Doulos Discovery Ministries\r\nPO Box 3080\r\nBurnsville, MN 55337</p>\r\n<small><b>Donations are TAX DEDUCTIBLE</b>, as they are made to Doulos Discovery Ministries – a registered 501(c)3 US not-for-profit – then distributed to staff. Receipts are mailed to donors 3 times/year and year-end giving receipts are provided at end of each tax year.</small>', 'Support', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '201-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-03-06 13:22:55', '2013-03-06 13:22:55', '', 201, 'http://josiahsprague.com/201-revision-17/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
