(725, 1, '2014-03-03 01:14:34', '2014-03-03 01:14:34', 'I am fundraising for a salary of $920/month which enables me to participate in <a onclick="javascript:_gaq.push([''_trackEvent'',''outbound-article'',''http://doulosdiscovery.org'']);" href="http://doulosdiscovery.org/about/">the mission of Doulos</a> to help educate and disciple students in the Dominican Republic. Help me do that by supporting me monthly!\r\n\r\n<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick" /><input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="VRLUK2XKLFW7N" /><input type="hidden" name="on0" value="Monthly Support for Josiah Sprague" /><select name="os0"><option value="$10/month">$10/month</option><option value="$15/month">$15/month</option><option value="$20/month">$20/month</option><option value="$25/month">$25/month</option><option selected="selected" value="$50/month">$50/month</option><option value="$100/month">$100/month</option><option value="$150/month">$150/month</option><option value="$200/month">$200/month</option><option value="$250/month">$250/month</option></select><input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="USD" /><button class="btn btn-primary btn-large" name="submit" type="submit">Sponsor Me Now</button>\r\n\r\n</form>If you want to donate offline or support me with a one-time donation, see the <a href="#give">bottom of this page for more information</a>.\r\n<h2>Tangible Support</h2>\r\nIf you’d like to support me in the form of a tangible item or gift, check out <a href=" http://amzn.com/w/3TYMJURCO73GE">my Amazon Wishlist</a> for a few ideas. Here are a few other things I need that you could support me with;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a onclick="javascript:_gaq.push([''_trackEvent'',''outbound-article'',''http://www.adobe.com'']);" href="http://www.adobe.com/products/creativesuite/production.edu.html">Adobe CS6 Production Premium</a> (Mac)</li>\r\n	<li>$3000 Support Account Buffer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id="goal">A Breakdown</h2>\r\nHere’s an estimated breakdown of my monthly needs, so you have an idea of what your donations are going towards.\r\n<table class="table table-striped">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Need</th>\r\n<th>Estimated Amount</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tithe</td>\r\n<td>$92</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Rent</td>\r\n<td>$180</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Food</td>\r\n<td>$165</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cell Phone</td>\r\n<td>$15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mail</td>\r\n<td>$5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Insurance, Taxes and Fees</td>\r\n<td>$193</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Miscellaneous</td>\r\n<td>$45</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>School Loans</td>\r\n<td>$60</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Plane Tickets</td>\r\n<td>$165</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Total</th>\r\n<th>$920</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2 id="give">Ways to Give</h2>\r\n<b>If you want to sponsor me monthly,</b> you can give automatically via direct deposit. To do so, download the <a onclick="javascript:_gaq.push([''_trackEvent'',''download'',''http://josiahsprague.com/pdf/JosiahSpragueDonation.pdf'']);" href="http://josiahsprague.com/pdf/JosiahSpragueDonation.pdf">direct donation form</a> and mail it to the <a href="http://josiahsprague.com/support/#address">Minesota Doulos address</a>, below, along with your first check. Alternatively, you can set up your bank account to automatically send a check to that address every month. If you would prefer to donate online, you can set up a monthly donation via PayPal, <a href="http://josiahsprague.com/support/#paypalform">above</a>.\r\n\r\n<b>If you want to support me with a one time donation,</b> you can send a check to the Minnesota Doulos address, or donate online via <a onclick="javascript:_gaq.push([''_trackEvent'',''outbound-article'',''http://doulosdiscovery.org'']);" href="http://doulosdiscovery.org/support/donate/">the donation page on the Doulos website</a>.\r\n\r\nPlease make all checks payable to <i>Doulos Discovery Ministries</i> and, for tax purposes, please be sure to include a note along with your check indicating that the donation is for Josiah Sprague (it is best if this is a separate note, rather than being written on the memo line).\r\n\r\nPlease send Direct Donation forms and checks to:\r\n<p id="address">Doulos Discovery Ministries\r\nPO Box 3080\r\nBurnsville, MN 55337</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Contact Me</h2>\r\nIf you have any questions or you want to get in touch with me, I can be reached via email at info<span style="display: none;">0000</span><span style="display: none;">0000</span><span style="display: none;">0000</span>@<span style="display: none;">0000</span>josiahsprague<span style="display: none;">0000</span>.<span style="display: none;">0000</span>com.\r\n\r\n<small><b>Donations are TAX DEDUCTIBLE</b>, as they are made to Doulos Discovery Ministries – a registered 501(c)3 US not-for-profit – then distributed to staff. Receipts are mailed to donors 3 times/year and year-end giving receipts are provided at end of each tax year.</small>\r\n<h2>Referral Links</h2>\r\nI supplement my support through money raised through referral sites and links. Here are some referral links that I’ve set up. If you’re interested in these products, you can support me by using the links below.\r\n\r\nBudgeting Software – Get a <a onclick="javascript:_gaq.push([''_trackEvent'',''outbound-article'',''http://ynab-coupon-code.com'']);" href="http://ynab-coupon-code.com/">discount on You Need a Budget</a>.\r\n\r\nAccounting Software – <a onclick="javascript:_gaq.push([''_trackEvent'',''outbound-article'',''http://fresh-books-accounting.com'']);" href="http://fresh-books-accounting.com/">FreshBooks Online Accounting Software</a>', 'Support', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '201-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-03 01:14:34', '2014-03-03 01:14:34', '', 201, 'http://josiahsprague.com/201-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
