(735, 1, '2014-03-04 18:57:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<h1>Job Opportunities</h1>\nAre you looking to stretch the limits of your comfort zone and passport? Do you want to use your God-given gifts and talents creatively and experientially to empower our students?\n\nWe have a number of opportunities available for teachers and staff who are passionate about Jesus, serving and loving those around them. Be a part of <a>our mission and vision</a>, check out our open positions below.\n<h2>Teaching Opportunities</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>Art Teacher</li>\n	<li>High School Science Teacher</li>\n	<li>Elementary ESL Instructor</li>\n	<li>Bible Teacher</li>\n	<li>Kindergarten Teaching Assistant</li>\n	<li>Adult English Teacher</li>\n	<li>Student Teaching (check with your university for compatibility)</li>\n</ul>\n<a href="ttp://doulosdiscovery.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/Doulos-Teacher-Application.zip">Teacher Application</a>\n<a href="http://doulosdiscovery.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/InternApp.zip">Student Teacher Application</a>\n<h2>Other Opportunities</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>Expedition Specialist</li>\n	<li>Media Specialist</li>\n	<li>Elementary Vice Principal</li>\n	<li>Secondary Vice Principal</li>\n	<li>Site Operations Supervisor</li>\n	<li>Work Team Host Internship</li>\n	<li>Construction Internship</li>\n	<li>Marketing Internship</li>\n	<li>Grant Writing Internship</li>\n</ul>\n<a href="http://doulosdiscovery.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/StaffApp.zip">Staff Application</a>\n<a href="http://doulosdiscovery.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/InternApp.zip">Internship Application</a>\n<h3>Qualifications</h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>Love for Jesus and a desire to grow and be stretched while loving on kids and their families</li>\n	<li>Teaching positions require a degree in Education and teaching certification required</li>\n	<li>Some positions are responsible for raising support of approximately $20,000 USD/year</li>\n	<li>Some positions may require Spanish proficiency</li>\n</ul>\nIf you or someone you know is interested in working at Doulos and would like more information, please contact us. Even if you don’t see the position you’re looking for listed here, we’re eager to give you an opportunity to serve the Lord here with your gifts.', 'Your New Page', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2014-03-04 18:57:33', '2014-03-04 18:57:33', '', 0, 'http://josiahsprague.com/?page_id=735', 0, 'page', '', 0),
